    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/f88a41dbbc9fbbde3688af4788f0e859.poster.avif?t=1765674357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/f88a41dbbc9fbbde3688af4788f0e859.webm?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/f88a41dbbc9fbbde3688af4788f0e859.mp4?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ZOMBI ROCKSTAR is a 2D platform hack and slash video game that will make a hellish riff unleashing the old school + rock + zombie epidemic through a fast-paced and frenetic story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/6fd0425ae83ffa962043aae4e4894b83.avif?t=1765674357\" width=600 height=930 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Punkrocker send deadly riffs to the zombies... the vibration and power of punk music will drive them crazy and destroy them. The environment will be one of your best weapons, destroy vehicles, barricades, tombstones and a host of other environmental elements that will damage the hordes of zombies that try to stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/7d61449156c7c87abe38119776f6222f.poster.avif?t=1765674357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/7d61449156c7c87abe38119776f6222f.webm?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/7d61449156c7c87abe38119776f6222f.mp4?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll use unique moves in strategic combos to charge up your electric guitar and use the ultimate musical trick that will make all the zombies around you dance. And remember, stay undefeated in damage to earn a radio with power ups that will save your winning streak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/3f069f750955189312077473a413c135.poster.avif?t=1765674357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/3f069f750955189312077473a413c135.webm?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/3f069f750955189312077473a413c135.mp4?t=1765674357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The decision is in your hands and in your brain... The die is cast, the zombies are waiting in the darkness... What are you waiting for to unleash rock, the best antidote against the undead? How will you do it? YOU ALREADY HAVE THE GUYS TO DO IT!!! Keep rocking, fast fingers, show that you are a gentleman with your girl and survive the zombie apocalypse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309880/extras/348c68ebb058440420fef160af327aa2.avif?t=1765674357\" width=680 height=918 /></span></p>",
